# Cursor Rules for MVP ChatStream Project

## Project Overview
This is a real-time chat application MVP built with React + TypeScript (client) and Node.js + Express + Socket.IO (server).

## Specialized Rules
- Socket.IO specific rules and best practices are defined in `.cursor/rules/socketio-rule.mdc`

## Tech Stack & Configuration
- **Frontend**: React + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind CSS
- **Backend**: Node.js + Express + Socket.IO
- **State Management**: Zustand (client-side)
- **Docker**: Node.js 20-alpine
- **Development**: Hot reload support in containers

## Key Development Standards
- Use TypeScript strict mode
- Follow React best practices (proper prop typing, error boundaries)
- Optimize performance (memo, dependency arrays, cleanup)
- Ensure Socket.IO compatibility in Docker environment